Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.77,0:22:22.52,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:28.15,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.15,0:22:31.11,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings messed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:33.99,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:39.18,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.50,0:22:46.09,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.09,0:22:51.47,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:58.35,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:04.77,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.84,0:23:13.96,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.96,0:23:19.16,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.16,0:23:22.21,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.21,0:23:25.25,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.25,0:23:30.78,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.39,0:01:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The midnight express bus \Nwas carrying me from New York to Boston.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.58,0:01:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dear Maki, as you've probably figured out, \NI am heading to Boston now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.10,0:01:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Striving to get to the US Pro Circuit, \NTodo will participate in a local tournament there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's one more person now. \NInspired by Todo's burning enthusiasm,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.61,0:01:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and thus decided to become a tournament challenger as well, \NMidorikawa Ranko is accompanying us now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We should arrive in Boston tomorrow morning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Both Todo and Midorikawa are now following the example of the rest of the passengers and sleep soundlessly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,While we rush through the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, this darkness right now is not being stared \Nby anyone else but the bus driver and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't get to sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For some reason, \NI can't sleep at all, Maki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Todo and Midorikawa are riding that bus \Nbecause they have their own, clearly defined goals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.31,0:02:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Comparing myself to them, I can't help but to keep asking myself, why on Earth am I going to Boston, and what will I do there?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.54,0:02:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These thoughts are what deprives me of sleep.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was finally able to meet with Todo. And I can't say \Nthat I'm unhappy to be riding this very this bus with him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.47,0:02:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Say, Maki... Maki?\NI'm not doing something wrong, do I?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.98,0:02:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not mistaking now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:53.00,Default,,0,0,100,,{\an8\bord4\blur15\3c&HAC907F&\t(0,1000,\bord0\blur1)\c&HFEFEFD&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\3a&H2D&\fscx184\fscy156}Episode 7
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.89,Default,,0,0,120,,{\b0\fs30\blur1\fnVerdana\bord0.8\c&HE1E4E4&\1a&H11&}Boston
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon arrival, Todo just threw his luggage into the room \Nand went out for roadwork immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.38,0:03:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We can only envy such a fervor for the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My, that's much fresher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.37,0:03:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa, do you mind if I have a little nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. It's a little too early anyway. \NBesides, you don't have to prepare for the tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning to find us a court for the practice today, \Nmake arrangements and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.35,0:03:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's time for breakfast, \NI'll wake you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The bus was uncomfortable, \Nno wonder you didn't get any sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear that. \NCalmed by your warm words, I'll have just a little bit more...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to give you this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't take your racket with you, did you? \NSo I'm giving you my spare one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I need an opponent. You won't refuse to play with me \Nfor the first time in a while, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are you in New York?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's complicated...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.30,0:05:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't expect that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.91,0:05:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's a surprise for sure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.25,0:05:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry. I just... \NSo much wanted to see you, no matter what.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oka...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was so surprising!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.63,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa, judging by your play, \None could never tell you've turned southpaw just recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good. When I was playing with my right, \Nthe power was times more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't agree on that point! Your serve, your forehand and your ball drive were no worse than before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.03,0:05:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not in the shape yet \Nto compete with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a single clue regarding what kind of stuff \Nis happening right now in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But haven't autumn tennis season \Nstarted a week or two ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that instead of making the best of your youth, \Nyou are wasting your time training here with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like moralizing, \Nbut don't you think something's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat too much, I'm not waiting for you to answer. Everyone has their own reasons for whatever they are doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is entitled \Nto be where they want and when they want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s certainly not for me \Nto tell others about being selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it seems to me that this time you've accumulated quite a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much pain you experience along the way, \Nyou should never use it as an excuse to give yourself an advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.92,0:06:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You should never try to chase the other party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, you yourself \Nshould give advantage to the other party.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been living by this principle for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I give the advantage to the other party and start waiting. And I wait patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Although sometimes the other party ends up leaving for somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.45,0:06:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Advantage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.08,0:07:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Not bad, Oka! \NWhat a great ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks! \NI am very grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At such moments...\NAt moments like this one, I wish the time would just stop!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hotel is in about 5 kilos from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we end our training \Nwith the scenic Tour de Boston ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree. \NLet's ride!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The first to arrive gets $ 1. \NHowever, the other two will pay for the winner's dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I want just a dessert with coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a positive okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.58,0:07:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.67,0:07:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! \NThe start is supposed to be simultaneous! Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.19,0:08:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's just the three of us, Maki. \NStill I'm so exceedingly happy, Maki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I feel that I'm no longer alone. These wonderful moments \Nwe've been through today, I could never forget!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.23,0:08:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While riding my bike \Nalongside the man I love...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't help forgetting about everything and SCREAM with delight, not minding whoever else is thinking this sunset city drove me crazy!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.77,0:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so glad Maki. If only you knew \Nhow glad I am that I was finally able to see Todo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thank you, Maki. \NMore than whenever.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Come to think of it, Oka, \Nyou should also participate with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Me and you in one team. Good thing we still have enough time \Nto sign up for this tournament doubles entry matches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.02,0:09:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The duo of such unknown pros as we are will positively put the locals to flight! Well? Isn't it a fine idea? Don't thou think?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We both happened to be in America now. \NIsn't it a fine chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.49,0:09:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But please, think again. I was not planning to stay here for long in the first place. I need a lot of stuff done...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the issue? Is it money?\NHotel accommodations?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, thou can consider that problem solved now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Slow down a bit there, player Midorikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.92,0:09:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.44,0:09:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka's full-time coach Mr. Katsura, \Nquite hot-tempered one, is waiting her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, such matters \NOka should not be deciding on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll call him! Trust me. \NWe'll easily reach a compromise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no worries! If Munakata's sister is in charge, \Neven his heart will descend.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep in mind that I know Daigo \Never since I first went to high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Plus all the stuff I've heard about him from Jin, \NI know him like the back of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't seem like I drank that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,However fine your idea is,\Nit can't be incarnated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.62,0:10:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Oka takes part in this tournament, her amateur qualification is no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,After returning to Japan, Oka will no longer be able to participate in amateur events.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.63,0:10:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it won't be about Mr. Katsura only. \NMadame Butterfly is also unlikely to get very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Tennis will be tennis. Pro or amateur - doesn't matter. \NNo difference, no at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa, are you feeling well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say nonsense. Chattering like this with you two can last forever and never make me even a bit tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.54,0:10:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If ye excuse me, \NI'll be heading to the room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.36,0:10:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.36,0:10:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,- Goodnight! \N- Good... night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.84,0:11:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I am sincerely happy \Nthat I was able to meet you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, until yesterday \NI was feeling a little depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I have perked up \Nand inclined to do my best again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me know \Nhow you were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been fine all this time, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.52,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Without any trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... Without any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.41,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then... That's a great relief to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.54,0:11:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning! Is anyone home? It's Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in, it's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:12:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Big news, big news!\NWait... Where's Oka, actually?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a morning shower. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm not sure how to start, \Nbut Mr. Sayama called me from New York recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.98,0:12:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This evening our friend Chiba \Nmust arrive in Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Chiba is coming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But how did it happen?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Different things have happened in Japan recently, and I don't want Todo to know about all of them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Oka!\NWe're here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing is. \NIt's just a little cold here, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.55,0:13:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing fine here, Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.17,0:14:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But first, tell me, how did it happen? \NWhat brought you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.85,0:14:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... This and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Midorikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.62,0:14:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when Mr. Sayama reported that he also met Midorikawa here, \Nmy astonishment knew no bounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only reborn as a southpaw \Nbut also determined to become a pro as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking about it for a long time already. \NIt was Todo who gave me momentum to make up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've barely done anything significant since.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, you should not be up now at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she just caught a little cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain caught us by surprise during the practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.59,0:14:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,First thing in the morning we’ll go to the local hospital. \NShe has a severe fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That sure is inconvenient...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, if you excuse us, we'll be heading back to the room now. \NWill see you tomorrow, Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.49,0:14:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka, don't overwork yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:14:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tokyo Cup was \Ngracefully won by Madame Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.95,0:15:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Reckon she's working as hard as always. \NWell, and how's Oka doing, actually?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.18,0:15:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She didn't want to talk about anything related to the court, \Nthough I'd be happy to know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, \NI'm more worried about her than ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me, that to get to this point, Oka had to go through impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If Oka decided not to tell you, \Nthen I shouldn't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But something tells me, \Nshe's doing it for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It all started because you've lost all your matches here, \Nbut didn't say a word about it to us whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.73,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not only about Oka alone. Me with Ozaki, \NMadame Butterfly and the others, are worried about you no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The same way you've made Oka worry about you before, \Nyou're being treated now yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:16:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka pitifully lost her very first Tokyo Cup game \Nto a complete rookie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Moreover, she's forgone the repêchage match \Nin order to go see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you expect such a thing from her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,However difficult times she had before, \Nnever had she lost so miserably, refusing to give it another try!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.30,0:16:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm trying \Nto blame you alone for her confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.85,0:16:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This insincerity to both of you has brought minuses only. \NAnd it's wrong. It's completely wrong, Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maki, during the next three days \NI've been curing myself in the room and did my best to recover.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then, right to the Todo's first qualifying match day, \NI could finally go out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,First round, first set. \NTakayuki Todo versus Ed Kartrite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Service play - Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:17:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sadly, I had no other chance to talk to Todo, \Nsince in the last few days I was sleeping most part of the day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, here and now \NI can clearly feel Todo's determination about this match.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As if he was somehow \Nconveying this idea to the audience.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.07,0:17:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Almost like... If I was playing this match myself. Like if I was holding the racket myself now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.56,0:17:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the first time \NI'm feeling such a thirst for victory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,15-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.94,0:17:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,30-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.91,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,40-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to his recent New York matches, \Nhe has certainly become livelier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe Todo has finally remembered he was Japan Open champ once and decided to fight accordingly to his title.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.48,0:18:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the opponent is also a player, \Nwho won the East Coast Amateur Championship twice previously.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,40-15!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Their abilities are about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.43,0:18:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a match, \Nwhere victory and defeat are equally possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,However, Todo is still good at ball handling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter if he wins or loses, we won't see him weeping over his helplessness from now on, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sayama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.51,0:18:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Deuce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Deuce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Deuce!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.80,0:19:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Advantage: Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.95,0:19:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This was your first victory in America. \NAccept my congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,In the second round, in the third round, and of course, \Neven in the final round, keep doing your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.47,0:19:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.47,0:19:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... I think, tomorrow... \NI'm coming back to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.31,0:20:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I know I came to America without warning you. And I'm sure, I've caused a lot of nuisance for you, Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,However, even having that said, \NI still have one more request.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you win or lose, \Nplease keep telling me about it in letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.57,0:20:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Especially{\i0} if you lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And you too...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.75,0:20:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This way I can have no worries \Neven when you're far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.99,0:20:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, I decided to celebrate \NTodo's first victory in America with a bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And if in tomorrow's women's qualifiers \NMidorikawa will perform just as great,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,who knows how many more champagnes will I have to treat us with? However, these expenses I'd be happy to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Better not to expect similar success from me. \NIt's more of a trial for me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.76,0:20:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Todo said the other day, \Nyour southpaw ball is even sharper than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.76,0:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He really did?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we wait a little longer? \NFor these two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, we will! \NEven for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.42,0:21:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.97,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one here who should apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I was the first one \Nto deprive you of rest by my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I was happy with that, \Nbut I couldn't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be closing yourself off from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No... That's not the way for me henceforth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.64,0:21:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this time, \Nplease let me give you this one little advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Advantage, Oka...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Aikawa Maki here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.38,0:23:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, finally, you're back home!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.78,0:23:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.38,0:23:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And thanks for beatiful souvenirs for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.08,0:23:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But upon returning, you're engaged again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The tough university coach takes you under his authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.16,0:23:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Coach Katsura wasn't always that harsh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.36,0:23:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still must fight, Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Queen's Cup is coming, and you should be triumphal on it! \NTriumphal! Right, Hiromi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.00,0:24:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: "The Final Repechage Match."